<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <title>Blog Website</title>

    <style>
        body {
            margin: 40px;
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle farthest-corner at 10% 20%, rgba(176, 229, 208, 1) 42%, rgba(92, 202, 238, 0.41) 93.6%);
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 10px;
        }
        p{
            margin: 10px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
        }

        .form-group input {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .form-group textarea {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .form-group label{
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 8px 0;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 15px;
        }

        .card-title {
            padding: 10px 0;
        }

        .btn {
            margin: 5px 10px;
        }
        .card-body a{
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .card-body button{
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="mb-4">Personal Blog Website</h1>
        <p class="mb-4">Welcome to my personal blog website! This space is dedicated to sharing thoughts,
            ideas, and experiences on various topics that I am passionate about. Whether you're here to read,
            explore, or engage in meaningful conversations, I hope you find the content insightful and inspiring.
            Feel free to browse through the different sections, and don't hesitate to leave your comments and feedback.
            Your participation is what makes this blog a vibrant community of curious minds.</p>
            
        <p class="mb-4">I warmly invite you to contribute by writing and posting your own blogs. This platform is not just about
            my voice, but about creating a diverse and inclusive environment where everyone can share their unique
            perspectives.
            Whether you're an experienced writer or a newcomer, your stories and insights are valuable here. So, take a
            moment
            to pen down your thoughts, share your experiences, and let's build a rich tapestry of ideas together.
            Welcome once again,
            and happy blogging!</p>
        <a href="/articles/new" class="btn btn-success">Create Article</a>

        <% articles.forEach(article=>{%>
            <div class="card mt-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h4 class="card-title">
                        <%=article.title%>
                    </h4>
                    <div class="card-subtitle text-muted mb-2">
                        <%=article.createdAt.toLocaleDateString() %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-text mb-2">
                        <%=article.description%>
                    </div>
                    <a href="articles/<%=article.slug%>" class="btn btn-primary">Read More</a>
                    <a href="articles/edit/<%= article.id%>" class="btn btn-info">Edit</a>
                    <form action="/articles/<%=article.id %>?_method=DELETE" method="POST" class="d-inline">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger">Delete</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>

            <%})%>
    </div>
</body>

</html>